Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.99,0:00:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ouryou, your daughter is here to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.28,0:00:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.53,0:00:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but your father knows you're here and is happy to see you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.91,0:00:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't get discouraged.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.40,0:00:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.81,0:00:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's a lie. Everyone here is the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.40,0:00:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They don't notice anything. They don't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.60,0:00:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They don't think anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.72,0:00:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They are mere shells of their former selves,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.05,0:00:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}soon to disappear like the melting snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.70,0:00:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This epidemic leads innocent people to their deaths,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and yet, its pathogen will never be eradicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the disease called serenity,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.50,0:00:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a form of death that people have wished for.
