Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.48,0:02:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.28,0:02:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They first dismembered and cut open the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.46,0:02:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and then they used plastination to turn it into a human specimen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then they brought it right into the middle of town and displayed it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking you off this case, Kougami.{lol cop drama cliches}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.27,0:02:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... Gino?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't allow a detective who can't\N\N put aside his preconceived notions
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to be a part of the initial investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:02:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:02:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We still don't know if this is connected to the Specimen Case.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.89,0:02:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.87,0:03:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm on standby at my quarters, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.85,0:03:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.43,0:03:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Tsunemori.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.61,0:03:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that you're aware of the circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch Kougami at all times and make sure he doesn't do anything stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.53,0:03:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll be your job during this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll summarize the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The dismembered body found in a park in Daikanyama, Shibuya ward
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,belonged to Kuzuhara Satsuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.72,0:03:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,who was a student at Ousou Academy, a private college for girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.89,0:03:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She went missing a week ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ousou Academy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.27,0:03:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...where Touma Kouzaburo, the suspect in the Specimen Case, worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.01,0:03:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The body was eroded by a special kind of chemical,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.78,0:03:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and the protein was converted into plastic form.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:04:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Analysis confirmed that the chemical used was the same one used in the case three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more than likely that these cases share the same culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.90,0:04:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So after three years, the mysterious killer returns, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.13,0:04:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Gino! Was it really okay to take Ko off the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been investigating the Specimen Case all this time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He might've been able to find us some new leads.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.56,0:04:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I've read his report.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's completely delusional.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.61,0:04:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Kougami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.53,0:04:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got the sparring program on the highest difficulty level!{fists only. final destination}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.38,0:04:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really human, Kougami?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.97,0:05:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.00,0:05:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, all it takes is one Paralyzer and I'm out like a light.{damn son}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just your average, weak human.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet the Property Management Division's gonna give you hell for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Not my fault their system's a piece of crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.85,0:05:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something on my face?{sup shirt}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.86,0:05:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.28,0:05:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You already get provided with a powerful weapon like the Dominator,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,so do you really have to engage in this much combat training?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Our weapons are powerful, but it's for that very reason
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.73,0:05:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,that their users have to be even stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.93,0:05:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, the Dominator doesn't kill people. I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.77,0:05:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to keep that in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.65,0:06:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to feel the pain here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.24,0:06:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to teach me something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.00,0:06:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't wanna be in a situation where {\i1}you{\i0} have to fire the Dominator.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,To start with, please wipe yourself down and put a shirt on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about the unsolved case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Public Safety Bureau Special Case 102.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.85,0:06:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked into it. Sorry to pry into your past.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.48,0:06:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you apologizing for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.22,0:06:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not angry with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.57,0:06:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I be angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's an old homicide case that claimed the life of one of my subordinates?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's been three years and we're no closer to solving it than when we began?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.16,0:06:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No reason to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I got angry at anyone, it'd be myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,In that homicide case, I didn't even come close to finding the mastermind
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.47,0:07:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,who'd been pulling the strings behind Touma Kouzaburo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.24,0:07:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think the same guy's behind this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.42,0:07:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.66,0:07:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still possible that this is just an elaborate copycat crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's definitely worth looking into.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been taken off the case, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.43,0:07:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.81,0:07:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna cause Gino too much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.69,0:07:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying, there's a way to handle these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We can find a good pretext to create a situation where they'd need us back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.67,0:07:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that really possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.71,0:07:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It is. Just wait and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.07,0:07:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of person was Enforcer Sasayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a real piece of work.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.69,0:07:51.70,md,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.05\blur2\an4\c&H365B4C&\frz88.75\b1\fscx138\fscy126\pos(1179,533)}A
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:51.70,md,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\an8\c&H50B386&\b1\p1\frz354.7\pos(1182,494)\fscx53\fscy40\clip(1159,430,1210,611)}m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a womanizer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.42,0:07:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost count of how many times he tried to grab Karanomori and Kunizuka's butts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.69,0:08:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He got slugged every time, but he never seemed to learn his lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.26,0:08:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He had a short fuse too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Once he got upset, there was nothing anyone could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.04,0:08:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, he went to the house of a guy who got flagged by a Hue Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.86,0:08:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,When he stepped inside, this guy was on top of a woman he had kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.05,0:08:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasayama almost killed the guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.98,0:08:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I was an Inspector at the time, I stopped him,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.57,0:08:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but deep down, I thought that he was a funny guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. That violent, womanizing bastard was a real funny guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,At the very least, I never expected he'd die that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see the picture of his body?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We found it underneath a Holographic display.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.66,0:08:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.68,0:08:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what kind of display it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.95,0:08:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.06,0:08:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an ad by a pharmaceutical company.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,"Our safe stress care will transport you to a world without suffering."
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.43,0:09:06.85,md,,0,0,0,,{\fay0.36\blur1.2\c&H344745&\fscx77\fscy60\pos(141,416.8)}A
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:06.85,md,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\an8\c&H5A7F7B&\b1\p1\fscx21\fscy27\pos(142,408)\clip(m 127 428 l 155 436 155 412 130 406)}m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.96,0:09:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Analysis showed that before Sasayama was turned into a specimen,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,he was dismembered while he was still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.60,0:09:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like the culprit was sending a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.14,0:09:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,"Life is nothing but suffering."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.22,0:09:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted the bastard who did that to Sasayama to meet the same end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.38,0:09:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I started feeling that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,my career as an Inspector was over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.55,0:09:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any regrets?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't regret my own actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But the thing is... the case is still unsolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.15,0:09:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to find the accomplice who helped Touma Kouzaburo three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.34,0:09:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there any leads that we can still use?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.17,0:09:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a picture that Sasayama took,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.74,0:09:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,though it's pretty blurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.67,0:09:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It was saved on the terminal that Sasayama used.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This man? Did you find out what his name was?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.46,0:10:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The picture's filename was...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.10,0:10:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,"Makishima."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.72,0:10:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They found Kuzuhara Satsuki dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.51,0:10:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshika has been absent from school since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.39,0:10:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.93,0:10:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}am{\i0} listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.74,0:10:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just Ookubo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that Yamaguchi Masami in Class B has been absent, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.88,0:10:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like there's trouble brewing at the Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"So"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's trouble, the first thing you should do is stay out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.60,0:10:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't gossip, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.68,0:10:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.48,0:10:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel that careless actions could put us in serious danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.61,0:10:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been friends with Yoshika since we were kids, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:11:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouryou Rikako.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.53,0:11:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ookubo was really crazy about her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.17,0:11:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And she seemed to be interested in Ookubo as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ask her, she might know something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.81,0:11:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There's this quote from Kierkegaard that my father liked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"Because man is superior to animals,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.50,0:11:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,in other words, because man is the self, and spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.76,0:11:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,man can be in despair."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.07,0:11:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you know despair, you cannot know hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.22,0:11:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My father used dismembered bodies as the subject of many of his drawings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because they symbolize the contradictory nature of the self.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.13,0:11:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I had great respect for my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He was aware of his obligation as an artist
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.53,0:11:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and continued to focus intently on using his creations to enlighten people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I think even now that he was a great artist indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I simply can't forgive him for abandoning that duty halfway through.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, my father passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.77,0:12:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been as good as dead for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.82,0:12:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,but finally even his heart gave in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.08,0:12:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.94,0:12:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.04,0:12:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I, his daughter, will carry out my father's duty together with you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that's wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,, It's exciting, isn't it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshika?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.29,0:12:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Eustress deficiency cerebral infarction.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.62,0:12:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's not the official name for the illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It is said to be the real cause of most deaths that are declared as{until shin no kata wa}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,"heart failure from unknown cause."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.48,0:12:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard of it. They say that it's a side effect of excessive stress care.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:13:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,For some time, it's been understood that moderate stress has beneficial effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.18,0:13:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, it stimulates the immune system.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,As they say, it serves as motivation in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You could even call it a reason for living.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,However, once Psycho-Pass checks became routine,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.18,0:13:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,people have found their sense of stress numbed so heavily that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.80,0:13:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,we started to see patients who couldn't even recognize stimulation itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Once that happens, they're like living corpses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.97,0:13:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon their autonomic nervous system stops functioning on its own
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and their vital functions shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.67,0:13:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.70,0:13:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So humans now care for themselves to the point that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.14,0:13:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,they've actually regressed as living beings, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.37,0:13:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact of the matter is,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.79,0:13:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,as much as our medical system has advanced,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.19,0:13:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,statistically, the average lifespan is actually decreasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this data will probably never be made public, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.82,0:13:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.59,0:14:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,In this era, everything that could be considered a reason to live has died out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.79,0:14:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No one tries to talk seriously about what life should be like anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.30,0:14:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The father of Ouryou Rikako, the girl I mentioned earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,had eustress deficiency as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.91,0:14:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouryou Rouichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.32,0:14:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,At some point, he was a predominant illustrator.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.70,0:14:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you heard of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.65,0:14:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I don't have much knowledge of the art world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He possessed a prodigious talent for drawing cruel, vivid nightmares using girls' bodies as motifs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.20,0:14:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,However, he himself was a man of quite strict morality.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.73,0:14:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not uncommon for there to be a disconnect between the creator
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.26,0:14:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and the impression their creations give.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.96,0:14:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But in Rouichi's case, there was a firm ideology there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:14:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,According to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.44,0:14:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,by becoming firmly aware of the cruelty
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.64,0:15:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,that hides in the dark depths of the human heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,humans can foster the common sense, ability to reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.83,0:15:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and goodwill to control that cruelty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.00,0:15:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He viewed his creative efforts as a means to enlighten the populace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,From what you say, he sounds like quite the saint.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the spread of Psycho-Pass assessments
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.36,0:15:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,ended this role that he had decided for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,People don't have to control themselves anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.70,0:15:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, they can now maintain their mental health through machine assessments.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.42,0:15:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,that Rouichi welcomed this technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.65,0:15:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever the means,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.34,0:15:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,his ideal of humanity having healthy and sound minds had been realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.12,0:15:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result, though, his mission ended and his life lost its meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.31,0:15:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.86,0:16:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought all artists were the same,\N concerned only with fame and wealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he too probably had inner conflicts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.37,0:16:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But in order to solve them,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.07,0:16:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,he used all kinds of state-of-the-art stress care methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,His daughter Rikako tells me that he was so dependent on them
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.08,0:16:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that you could call it an addiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.51,0:16:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,he became a living corpse who couldn't even sit up from his bed, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She loved her father so much that I'm sure
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.32,0:16:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,she couldn't forgive that which took him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.89,0:16:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as if Ouryou Rouichi was killed twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.42,0:16:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,First, his talent was killed by science and technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.92,0:16:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, his soul was killed by society.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.77,0:16:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In short, you mean this girl is committing crimes to get revenge for her father?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.38,0:16:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.79,0:16:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope she finds some meaning beyond revenge, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Choe Gu-Sung?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.55,0:17:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That was quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.56,0:17:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I do wonder how Mr. Makishima knew that there was a place like this inside the Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.83,0:17:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems this used to be a generator room that powered a recycling boiler,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but when the Academy was renovated, it disappeared from the blueprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.44,0:17:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How slipshod, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.14,0:17:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So where are the chemicals?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.81,0:17:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Deliveries aren't usually my thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but the payment this time is quite generous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.14,0:17:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention I get to help out a cute young lady like yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.09,0:18:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I hardly have reason to complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Where does Mr. Makishima get weird stuff like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.05,0:18:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He did mention that they were leftover stockpiles from past festivities.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.85,0:18:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know who made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.21,0:18:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The person must've thought that entertaining Makishima would be a lot more worthwhile
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.97,0:18:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,than getting a patent for this weird chemical or selling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He does seem to attract geniuses that have gone astray.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.53,0:18:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're one of them, right, Choe Gu-Sung?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.35,0:18:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.49,0:18:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,but when I'm with him, I feel like I'm reliving my childhood or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.78,0:18:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I start to wonder what mischief we should get up to in order to shake up society,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and my thoughts become consumed with those ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I know the feeling.{i know that feel bro}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.55,0:19:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys prepare toys,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.00,0:19:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and we, mischievous children that we are, use those toys to create a stir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.99,0:19:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is fun, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, us toy manufacturers
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,have enough fun just watching what you brats do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.28,0:19:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'd say they're probably discovering my second prank right about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep an eye on the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.73,0:19:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.85,0:19:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You always leave before the really fun stuff begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.91,0:19:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a shame you miss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I don't do too well around blood and stuff, so I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.24,0:19:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A second one...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.40,0:19:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is really Touma Kouzaburo's doing, that makes it the sixth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.56,0:20:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what was it that you wanted to ask me, Kawarazaki Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.08,0:20:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Yoshika...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.53,0:20:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about Ookubo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.79,0:20:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been absent from school for the last three days in a row, so... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.71,0:20:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're worried. You care about your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.32,0:20:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been friends since we were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.90,0:20:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendship between girls is wonderful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it might end up being a very exciting motif.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.03,0:20:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.29,0:20:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It might also be a good addition to my Yoshika exhibition, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.68,0:21:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A touching reunion with your childhood friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.03,0:21:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an emotionally stirring scene, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It really makes me cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.48,0:21:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to reenact this moving scene in a place where more and more people can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.22,0:21:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it really is the fate of artists to be struck by such inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:46.41,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,2200)\blur1}It seems all fairy tales {\alpha&HFF&}are dead
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.67,0:21:50.39,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,900)\blur1\alpha&HFF&}It seems {\alpha&H00&}all fairy tales are dead
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.14,0:21:55.74,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,900)\blur1}In a hospital ward of brick stones
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.60,0:22:00.83,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,900)\blur1}my voice is too coarse to sing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.82,0:22:05.95,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,900)\blur1}Outside in the foggy haze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.16,0:22:11.55,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,900)\blur1}a red moon glows
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.50,0:22:16.95,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,900)\blur1}Look at me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.77,0:22:22.47,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,900)\blur1}Do not avert your gaze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.85,0:22:26.79,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}Behind black bars
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.59,0:22:29.47,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}I was born
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.27,0:22:31.91,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}I wish there were a punishment for evil
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.71,0:22:34.78,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}Always I need you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.58,0:22:37.45,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}Now, grant us justice
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.25,0:22:39.97,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}before chaos takes us all
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.77,0:22:44.24,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}Pay the price of fate and let us go together,
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.92,0:22:49.99,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,500)\blur1}nameless beasts
